            <lg xml:id="TK577">
<l>kaṇṇōṭṭa millavar kaṇṇilar kaṇṇuṭaiyār </l>
<l> kaṇṇōṭṭa miṉmaiyu mil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Men without kind looks are men without eyes those who (really) have eyes are also not devoid of kind looks.</l>
            </lg>
